            <div type="transcript" id="F1364B">
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>Escape is such a<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 thankful Word </l>
                    <l>I often in the Night </l>
                    <l>Consider it unto<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 myself </l>
                    <l>No spectacle in sight </l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>Escape - it is the Basket</l>
                    <l>In which the Heart<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 is caught </l>
                    <l>When down some<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 awful Battlement </l>
                    <l>The rest of Life is<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 dropt - </l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>'Tis not to sight the<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 savior - </l>
                    <l>It is to be the saved -</l>
                    <l>And that is why I lay<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 my Head<app type="division"><lem><pb/></lem></app>
 </l>
                    <l>Opon this trusty word - </l>
                </lg>

            </div>     
